code: /**  * Return the full version string of the present Spring codebase,  * or {@code null} if it cannot be determined.  * @see Package#getImplementationVersion()  */ @Nullable public static String getVersion() {     Package pkg = SpringVersion.class.getPackage().     return (pkg != null ? pkg.getImplementationVersion() : null). }
